Real-Time Fun Face Filter with OpenCV 
A playful webcam app that detects faces in real-time using OpenCV and overlays fun filters—like hats or glasses—right on top of your head! Features include:

Live face detection with Haar cascades

Transparent PNG filter overlays positioned dynamically above detected faces

Toggle camera ON/OFF with a keyboard shortcut (c)

Clean exit with ESC key

Easily customizable to add your own filters or effects

Perfect for learning OpenCV basics while adding a touch of augmented reality fun!

